Here is what the OS does and what it should do.

Since we are creating an entire OS with the layout this is highly recommanded to make this entire thing structured and architecture.

All the Code of the OS Apps is under OS folder located at /OS

This is the sidebar Schema: [SidebarSchema.ts](mdc:OS/Layout/Sidebar/SidebarSchema.ts)

This is the entire AppSchema: [types.ts](mdc:OS/Layout/types.ts)

This is the Dialog Schema: [DialogSchema.ts](mdc:OS/Layout/Dialog/DialogSchema.ts)

Folder of Sidebar Located: ./OS/Layout/Sidebar

Folder of Dialog Located: ./OS/Layout/Dialog

Here is the form that uses in the OS which is used for the Dialog [Form.tsx](mdc:OS/Layout/Form.tsx)

Everything is ran within the [index.tsx](mdc:OS/Layout/index.tsx)

Here is an example of how to use InteractApp

First Example: [index.tsx](mdc:components/Tool/TodoList/index.tsx) and the provider of the todolist contains the appSchema [todolistProvider.tsx](mdc:components/Tool/TodoList/provider/todolistProvider.tsx)

import { useInteractApp } from "@OS/Provider/InteractAppProv";

<InteractApp appSchema={appSchema} className="p-3">
    <TabsContainer />
</InteractApp>

Here is the appSchema:
const appSchema: AppSchema = useMemo(() => {
return {
id: "hyperchotodolist",
name: "Todo List",
sidebar: {
sections: [
{
id: "tasks",
items: [
{
id: "myday",
title: "My Day",
icon: Sun,
isActive: currentTab === "myday",
onClick: () => handleTabChange("myday"),
},
{
id: "starred",
title: "Starred",
icon: Star,
isActive: currentTab === "starred",
onClick: () => handleTabChange("starred"),
},
{
id: "finished",
title: "Finished",
icon: SquareCheckBig,
isActive: currentTab === "finished",
onClick: () => handleTabChange("finished"),
},
{
id: "task",
title: "Tasks",
icon: ListChecks,
isActive: currentTab === "task",
onClick: () => handleTabChange("task"),
},
],
},
{
id: "lists",
title: "Lists",
items: [
...lists.map((list) => ({
id: list._id,
title: list.name,
icon: ListChecks,
isActive: currentTab === "list" && listId === list._id,
onClick: () => handleTabChange("list", list._id),
})),
{
id: "create-new-list",
title: "Create new list",
icon: Plus,
isDraggable: false,
onClick: handleCreateList,
},
],
type: "rowOrder+collapsible",
reorder: handleDragEndLists,
},
],
},
detail: {
animationKey: "todolist_detail",
body: (
<>
{!selectedTask ? (
taskLoading && <TodoDetailSkeleton />
) : (
<TaskDetails task={selectedTask} />
)}
</>
),
},
};
}, [lists, currentTab, listId, selectedTask, taskLoading]);

